==Useful Info==
'''White draconians''' are the [[cold]]-themed members of the [[list of draconians|draconian]] family. Their have cold breath attacks that can slow down [[cold blooded]] creatures. They can be found primarily in [[the Realm of Zot]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Cold resistance helps defend against their breath attacks.
*Unlike most draconians, they are not especially vulnerable to [[freezing]]-branded weapons, so consider bringing a backup brand if you intend to freeze your way through Zot.

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|their Cold Breath will do 3d22 damage.}}
*Prior to [[0.27]], they had [[Chilling Breath]] instead of [[Cold Breath]].
